 # File type mappings\n57: └── utils.py       # Utility functions\n58: ```\n59: \n60: ## License\n61: \n62: MIT License\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","title":"README.md","metadata":{"preview":"# Simple Local File Organizer\n\nA command-line utility that automatically organizes files in a directory into categorized folders based on file type.\n\n## Features\n\n- Automatically organize files into categories (Images, Documents, Videos, Archives)\n- Preview actions with dry-run mode\n- Simple command-line interface\n- Fast execution for large directories\n- Local-only operation (no external services)\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install -e .\n```\n\nOr run directly:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"time":{"start":1772917048133,"end":1772917048134}}}}
